        <h2>Why Alignment Matters</h2>
        <p>Proper wheel alignment ensures your vehicle drives straight, reduces uneven tire wear, and enhances overall safety. Misaligned wheels can cause tires to wear prematurely and reduce fuel efficiency. Regular alignment checks are essential for vehicle health.</p>
        <img src="file:///C:/Users/Kal Tire/Desktop/Alignment/Alignment Examples/tire-alignment-hero-learn-na-bst-web-consumer.jfif" alt="Professional Wheel Alignment">
