        <h2>When We Charge for Alignments</h2>
        <p>At Kal Tire, you are only charged for an alignment if:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>We need to make an adjustment to bring your alignment into specification.</li>
            <li>A suspension part needs to be replaced to ensure proper alignment.</li>
            <li>Your vehicle's alignment is already in specification, and no changes are required.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>This ensures transparency and fair pricing for our valued customers.</p>
